title: >>> The ClimaXX AWAITS
body_text:
The long awaited DODGEBALL 20 poster is finally here. Enjoy all the memories that dodgeball has given us in the past 4 months with this very special collage promotional poster.
The ClimaXX is indeed coming ...
Check out "DODGEBALL Promotional Posters" at
http://community.webshots.com/user/undertaker15yrs
for the "breaking-apart" of this very poster.
